{"tid":1222554,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"各位切忌鬆懈！要認清我地嘅目標！！！","createTime":"2019-06-14T12:53:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T13:00:28.000Z","uid":26557,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2c672d840a33860909ce180df8a26c2ca1ba84ce","tid":1222554,"uid":26557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:53:28.000Z","msg":"相信咁多位呢兩日都好疑惑點解冇會開<br />\n<br />\n下星期一二都唔開會<br />\n<br />\n建制派又放水話可以考慮<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">暫緩</span>修例<br />\n<br />\n好似有轉機咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係大家千其唔好因為咁樣而鬆懈！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地係要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">撤回惡法</span><br />\n<br />\n嚟緊仲有好長嘅路要行 希望咁多位巴絲可以互相扶持<br />\n<br />\n勿忘初衷！<br />\n<br />\n最後想多謝所有付出過嘅巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人要加油啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6569edd34d4d9f66c8d38d18cd5fdf5eaefab44","tid":1222554,"uid":5627,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:56:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b5d60caddd093e6c70866f911f9117d4c506c791","tid":1222554,"uid":26557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:00:28.000Z","msg":"自推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家要加油"}]}